    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those seeking a dedicated restoration project or a source for spare parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including several areas of rust, deep scratches, and fading paint. Mechanically, the car requires substantial work to be roadworthy, as it currently has engine issues and a worn-out suspension. The interior also reflects heavy use with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest significant time and resources into repairs.",
