    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. It suffers from major mechanical issues, specifically a failing transmission and an engine that struggles to start and stay running. The body has extensive damage, including deep rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and severely peeling clear coat. The interior is also heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is strictly an 'as-is' sale, ideal only for those seeking a project or a donor vehicle for parts.",
