    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're just ziping around town or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for its next adventure! It runs great and is looking for a new home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera represents a purist driving experience, powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus technology for optimized torque delivery. Power is managed through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle features a robust suspension geometry with McPherson struts up front and a sophisticated multi-link rear setup, providing exceptional lateral grip. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated rotors, showing excellent bite and minimal fade. This is a mechanically sound example ready for spirited canyon runs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
